{"tid":1757572,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post}要人!!!全民打擊選舉舞弊行動正式上線!!!","createTime":"2019-11-26T14:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T01:42:01.000Z","uid":116465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56e0c9503ea31fc2f45f1c360231ee001144ff67","tid":1757572,"uid":116465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">代號：棒打落水狗</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfqTwsE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwfqTwsE.jpg&h=bf44669b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>引言</ins></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKAz0pP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKAz0pP.jpg&h=6415b74c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孫子曰：乘勝追擊，棒打落水狗。<br />\n<br />\n沉溺於一刻小勝，<br />\n不但拖慢行軍，更會漸挫士氣。<br />\n而最重要的，係要對得住每一個尚未知生死，或已捱彈受辱的手足。<br />\n所以，我地呢次贏，就要贏到盡！<br />\n<br />\n會心一擊招式名稱：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你。有。舞。弊！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9O9PjE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9O9PjE.gif&h=561b7df1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>兵法第一步：搜證</strong></ins></span><br />\n基本上，你求其上google搵新聞，<br />\n已經可以搵到唔少，<br />\n而老夫都知你地懶，搵定左一堆以作參考。<br />\n<br />\n「一覆核多左二百票?」- 自由西 fb<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=468219683808808&amp;id=375375719759872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D468219683808808%26id%3D375375719759872&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx93jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=299f2c15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=468219683808808&amp;id=375375719759872</a><br />\n<br />\n美孚NGO派福袋 長沙灣酒吧派米<br />\nFact Check賄選疑雲 - 蘋果日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/arti