hkad_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=2c64d5cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191125&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60307890&amp;utm_source=email&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link</a><br />\n<br />\n僅輸兩票遭鄉黑圍 羅庭輝擬提呈請 - 蘋果日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191126/YZZ7TIPI7XQMC5BE2WOJHDNM2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191126%2FYZZ7TIPI7XQMC5BE2WOJHDNM2A%2F&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx93jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=bc9dfe7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191126%2FYZZ7TIPI7XQMC5BE2WOJHDNM2A%2F&h=2c6b6bc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191126/YZZ7TIPI7XQMC5BE2WOJHDNM2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，上網人人都識，<br />\n而全民動員既其中一個好處，<br />\n就係有機會接觸到現場的目擊證人，<br />\n甚至挖到幾條公眾傳媒都無既片或其他證據。<br />\n<br />\n所以，要叫埋你老公老婆男友女友，<br />\n阿哥阿嫂老豆老母契細佬，<br />\n姨媽姑姐uncle hi auntie同事Mary，<br />\n全民東張西望，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">挖佢d料挖佢老尾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins><strong>兵法第二步：成雲海</strong></ins></span><br />\n第一條最正統既門路，<br />\n當然係向選舉管理委員會投訴。<br />\n而詳細教學呢，已由香港第一投訴達人&rarr;<br />\n陳。雲。海提供左啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3248794391829339&amp;id=197517173623758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3248794391829339%26id%3D197517173623758&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx93jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=dadcaef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3248794391829339&amp;id=197517173623758</a><br />\n<br />\n曾聽說政府部門一聽到Henry Chan打黎，<br />\n就會嚇到標屎。<br />\n如果無啦啦多一百個雲海打去，<br />\n我會好擔心佢地既衛生狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v5gjskj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv5gjskj.jpg&h=3197c4bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">兵法第三步：藍雀行動</span></ins></strong><br />\n做完本地梗係出一出埠撚藍雀(Twitter)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OFrvy0R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOFrvy0R.png&h=cfeeac57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近半年，有唔少手足已累積豐富國際線經驗，<br />\n掌心雷作為香港土產，一定要好好推向全世界。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QR7KDtw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQR7KDtw.jpg&h=8f3ff0a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老夫唔識番文，<br />\n聽聞美國有所羅門 @SolomonYue<br />\n英國有天行者 @lukedepulford<br />\n咁多位御史一定比老夫更熟，<br />\n就將證據好好整合再翻譯，送比佢地睇吓啦。<br />\n#2019HKLocalElections #ElectoralFrand<br />\n#StandwithHK<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">兵法第四步：做啦懵撚！</span></ins></strong><br />\n唔係話投左個票，代議士就會奉旨幫你。<br />\n你連最基本搵佢投訴跟進都唔做，<br />\n咁樣對家就會永續行陰招，<br />\n而你就每次都嬲完一輪又正常過活。<br />\n<br />\n正所謂天生我才必有用，<br />\n你肯做佢肯做，力量自然就大。<br />\n自己做起，叫身邊人一齊做，<br />\n識設計整文宣，識英文打國際線，<br />\n鍵盤就打下投訴信或者幫老夫推下post，<br />\nshare出去都好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">完</span>"},{"pid":"703fb654d3ea8317c702342d481e0c2ffbd21e95","tid":1757572,"uid":116465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔怕自推 x 1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e7e71f0c7a4d6d028e804dc3e0cbb4a28ca5cd","tid":1757572,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/omEX1tT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FomEX1tT.jpg&h=57874f45&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrdqqVy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrdqqVy.jpg&h=1739302f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" da